      "content": "i mean, he's 72 so he gets tired easily. the flight was like 14 hours and he didn't sleep much. he's saying he just feels \"off\" and needs some water and a nap. you don't think it's anything serious, right? like, could it just be the jet lag or maybe some dehydration hitting him all at once?",
